<field>STAND.VM.KEY</field>
<desc>
            <p>The key for this file is designed to aid reporting of varition margins in the DX revaluation suite.</p>
            <p>  An example of key could be,</p>
            <p>  DXRVL9510900006*1*USD*10018</p>
            <p />
            <p>  DXRVL9510900006 - This is the key to the revaliation that         created the record.</p>
            <p>  1 - This is the exchange code for which this record         belongs.</p>
            <p>  USD - This is the currency of the margins held at the         exchange.</p>
            <p>  10018 - This is the customer/group or portfolio to which         the margins relate.</p>
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p />
            <p>  None</p>
        </desc>
